        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">water</ENAMEX>. Once they finish the lower grades, the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Niihau</ENAMEX> attend
