        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Kahoolawe</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Barren Kahoolawe</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">kah-ho-oh-law-vay</ENAMEX>) is a tiny
        island just off the southwest coast of <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Maui</ENAMEX>. Once inhabited by ancient
        Hawaiians, the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">island</ENAMEX> has since served as an <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">Alcatraz</ENAMEX> for <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">criminals</ENAMEX>, a
